&lt;li class=&quot;li6&quot;&gt;Complete work orders accurately and on time&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li7&quot;&gt;Perform inspections and basic repairs following SOPs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p5&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AV Systems Work&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;ul1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li6&quot;&gt;Work with AV components including sensors, diagnostics, and system checks under guidance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li6&quot;&gt;Capture logs, photos, and diagnostic data as required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li7&quot;&gt;Follow defined workflows for AV-related tasks and escalate issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p5&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SOP &amp;amp; Quality&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
