&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Lead operational incident response from an execution perspective, including classification, response coordination, and post-incident follow-up.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
